title: Good Omens 1x05: The Doomsday Option Reaction
author: Liam Catterson
comment: Crowley is such a loveable disaster demon. I love him so much. I just want to hug him and protect him for all the things that want to hurt him LOL He's such a soft precious demon.

"When he was a bit drunk"
A bit. Nooo. Really?????? ROFL

Love your reactions. To all of it but mostly to Crowley. Yup you're not the only one who love that little bastard 💖
Looking forward to next part. And NOT looking forward to it since it is the end. Don't want it to end

Croooowley, you sssexy sssnek. Or, that might just be me being a sucker for David Tennant overall. 

Did you notice that Aziraphale didn’t realise Crowley meant him when he said he lost his best friend? He’s such a lovable moron. In a way, they both are. Ineffable idiots. 😍
